mazes
Class Maze

java.lang.Object
  environment.AbstractEnvironmentSingle
      mazes.Maze
All Implemented Interfaces:
IEnvironment, IEnvironmentSingle, java.io.Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AliceMaze, LocalVisionMaze
public class Maze
extends AbstractEnvironmentSingle

Standard rectangular maze : each position is either free, a wall, a treasure. Reward is return when one reaches a treasure. It is up to you to add new types of positions, non-rectangular shapes ...

Author:
Francesco De Comite
